# Netscape HTTP Cookie File
# This is an EXAMPLE file. Replace values with your own exported cookies.
#
# How to export:
#   1. Log into https://music.youtube.com in Chrome/Chromium
#   2. Install "Get cookies.txt" (or "cookies.txt export") extension
#   3. Export as Netscape format
#   4. Save to a secure location (e.g. ~/.config/youtui/cookies.txt)
#
# IMPORTANT: The file must be raw Netscape format (tab-separated fields).
#            Do NOT add a "Cookie:" prefix. The parser reads the raw fields.
#
# Format: domain  flag  path  secure  expiration  name  value

.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	FALSE	1767225600	__Secure-3PSID	example_sid_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	FALSE	1767225600	__Secure-3PAPISID	example_apisid_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	FALSE	1767225600	__Secure-3PSIDCC	example_sidcc_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	FALSE	1767225600	__Secure-3PSIDTS	sidts-example_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	FALSE	1767225600	__Secure-3PAPISID	example_apisid_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	TRUE	1767225600	__Secure-1PSID	example_value_here
.music.youtube.com	TRUE	/	TRUE	1767225600	__Secure-1PSIDTS	sidts-example_value_here
